reviewText: I know this will sound kind of silly but...I really like the sound track to this video!  While the action in the video is entertaining {the ladies are quite attractive!}  The music  has a well match groove to the grinding that goes on in the video, which does work surprisingly well while doing other things, {wink wink!} I plan on buying the dvd before my vhs tape wears out.
This CD is just enough to get you in the mood, if you're not, and it isn't tacky.  I always liked the Playboy DVD's because they are done in good taste.
